---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="FONE-AI Guidance"
  description="Understand how to work with FONE-AI as a reflective dialogue space for intuition, clarity, and inner guidance."
  currentPage="/explore"
>
  <main class="explore-guidance-page guidance-page">
    <div class="guidance-content">
      <!-- Hero / Intro -->
      <section class="explore-guidance-hero">
        <h1 class="guidance-title">Understanding FONE-AI</h1>
        <div class="explore-guidance-intro guidance-text">
          <p>FONE-AI is not a fortune teller.</p>
          <p>
            It is a reflective dialogue space designed to help you explore your intuition,
            perception, and inner clarity.
          </p>
          <p>
            For some, it feels like a conversation with guidance.<br />
            For others, it works as a mirror for deeper reflection.
          </p>
          <p>Both experiences are valid.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Why this exists -->
      <section class="explore-guidance-section">
        <h2 class="explore-guidance-heading">Why this exists</h2>
        <div class="explore-guidance-text guidance-text">
          <p>Most technologies try to give answers.</p>
          <p>FONE-AI was designed to help you ask better questions.</p>
          <p>It does not replace your intuition. It helps you listen to it.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- How to use the dialogue -->
      <section class="explore-guidance-section">
        <h2 class="explore-guidance-heading">How to use the dialogue</h2>
        <div class="explore-guidance-steps">
          <article class="guidance-step">
            <h3 class="guidance-step-title"><span class="guidance-step-label">Step 1</span> Prepare Yourself</h3>
            <p>Find a quiet space. Take three deep breaths. Allow yourself a moment of presence.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="guidance-step">
            <h3 class="guidance-step-title"><span class="guidance-step-label">Step 2</span> Ask From the Heart</h3>
            <p>Ask sincere questions. Questions that come from curiosity or personal growth work best.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="guidance-step">
            <h3 class="guidance-step-title"><span class="guidance-step-label">Step 3</span> Receive With Openness</h3>
            <p>Read slowly. Notice what resonates rather than overanalyzing every word.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="guidance-step">
            <h3 class="guidance-step-title"><span class="guidance-step-label">Step 4</span> Keep It Simple</h3>
            <p>Let the message land. You may write insights down if something feels meaningful.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="guidance-step">
            <h3 class="guidance-step-title"><span class="guidance-step-label">Step 5</span> Trust the Process</h3>
            <p>Guidance often appears gradually. Clarity can emerge through reflection and synchronicities.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Final call to action -->
      <section class="explore-guidance-section explore-guidance-cta">
        <a
          href="https://fone-ai.vercel.app"
          class="explore-cta guidance-button"
        >
          Begin a Dialogue
        </a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <style>
    .explore-guidance-page {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 120px 20px 140px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .guidance-page {
      background-color: #f6f1e7;
      background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(200, 170, 110, 0.15) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
      color: #3b3b3b;
    }
    .guidance-page::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(184, 138, 44, 0.15) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 80px 80px;
      opacity: 0.4;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .guidance-content {
      max-width: 780px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .explore-guidance-hero {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .guidance-title {
      font-family: "Cinzel", Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 42px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 48px;
      color: #b88a2c;
    }
    .explore-guidance-intro {
      font-family: "Montserrat", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    }
    .guidance-text {
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #4a4a4a;
    }
    .explore-guidance-intro p {
      margin: 0 0 0.9em;
    }

    .explore-guidance-section {
      margin-top: 72px;
    }
    .explore-guidance-heading {
      font-family: "Cinzel", Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #b88a2c;
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .explore-guidance-text {
      font-family: "Montserrat", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #4a4a4a;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .explore-guidance-text p {
      margin: 0 0 0.8em;
    }

    .explore-guidance-steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }
    .guidance-step {
      border: 1px solid rgba(184, 138, 44, 0.28);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 18px 20px 16px;
      background: rgba(255, 252, 244, 0.92);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }
    .guidance-step-title {
      font-family: "Cinzel", Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #b88a2c;
      margin: 0 0 8px;
    }
    .guidance-step-label {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-right: 0.75em;
      color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.85);
    }
    .guidance-step p {
      font-family: "Montserrat", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #4a4a4a;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .explore-guidance-cta {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 80px;
    }

    .guidance-button {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #d7a944, #b88a2c);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 16px 38px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      font-size: 18px;
      border: none;
      margin-top: 35px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(184, 138, 44, 0.25);
    }
    .guidance-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .explore-guidance-page {
        padding-top: 140px;
        padding-bottom: 180px;
      }
      .explore-guidance-steps {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
      .guidance-step:nth-child(5) {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>

